{"tid":2288131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"示威者疑遭警毆打致死 白羅斯多個城巿週日示威悼念 人權組織指近千人被捕","createTime":"2020-11-16T09:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T09:33:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"136d39fa18790ecf9418c798a584bb0bf54e6bd1","tid":2288131,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:31:35.000Z","msg":"白羅斯多個城巿週日（15 日）再有數以千計民眾上街，除繼續要求總統盧卡申科下台，亦抗議一名示威者遭警察毆打、在拘留期間離世，他們燃點燭光並帶同白色鮮花悼念，要求政府查明死因。在首都明斯克，警方動用催淚彈及水炮車驅散示威者，據當地人權組織公布，當日全國有至少 928 人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據外媒引述目擊者報道，疑似便衣警員上週三（11 日）在明斯克法院外，試圖扯下代表反政府陣營的紅白色絲帶，一名 31 歲示威者 Roman Bondarenko 與他們爭執，他其後被帶上車拘捕。他的家屬後來在醫院找到他，他當時仍是昏迷狀態，直至上周四（12 日）因腦部受損離世，外界懷疑他在羈押期間被毆打。當地政府否認與他的死亡有關，指他的死因是民眾間毆鬥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB-%E7%99%BD%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%BF%E9%80%B1%E6%97%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%8C%87%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AF%2586%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E9%2580%25B1%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%25BF%25B5-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=db2a9396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AF%2586%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E9%2580%25B1%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%2582%25BC%25E5%25BF%25B5-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=08fa61f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB-%E7%99%BD%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%BF%E9%80%B1%E6%97%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%8C%87%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/</a>"},{"pid":"44f91b1883268dd91b5706e7ea048967f446ad6f","tid":2288131,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}